name: Tender (Submitted)
query:
SELECT
  `t0`.`name`,
  `t0`.`organization`,
  `t0`.`location`,
  `t0`.`tender_no`,
  `t0`.`status`,
  `t0`.`stage`,
  `t0`.`type`,
  `t0`.`submission_deadline`,
  `t0`.`owner`,
  `t0`.`company`
FROM `tabTender` AS `t0`
WHERE
  `t0`.`status` IN ('Submitted') AND NOT (
    `t0`.`stage` IN ('Contract Awarded')
  )
